In the mentioned formula < λ > was defined as mean diffusivity (MD). In addition, Axial diffusivity (AxD) was equal to λ1 (largest eigenvalue). Radial diffusivity (RD) values were defined through the following formula:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
